Title: Dual Actions for Chiral Bosons
Authors: Alexey Maznytsia, Christian R. Preitschopf and Dmitri Sorokin
Comments: Latex, 10 pp. Talk given at the International Workshop "Supersymmetry
  and Integrable Systems" (June 22-26,1998, Dubna, Russia) and at the Xth
  School-Seminar on Recent Problems in Theoretical and Mathematical Physics
  "VOLGA 10'98" (June 22-July 2, 1998, Kazan, Russia)
Report-no: HUB-EP-98/47
Journal-ref: Recent Problems in Physics.1998, pp.231-240, Ed. A.V. Aminova
  (Kazan, 1998)
\\
  We study duality properties of actions for chiral boson fields in various
space-time dimensions using D=2 and D=6 cases as examples. As a result we get
dual covariant formulations of chiral bosons.
